theorem upper (s : clopen_upper_set α) : is_upper_set (s : set α) :=
  s.upper'
#align upper upper
ext:
@[ext]
protected theorem ext {s t : clopen_upper_set α} (h : (s : set α) = t) : s = t :=
  SetLike.ext' h
#align ext ext
coe_top:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr⊤» -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_top : (↑(«expr⊤» : clopen_upper_set α) : set α) = univ :=
  rfl
#align coe_top coe_top
coe_sup:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⊔ » -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_sup (s t : clopen_upper_set α) : (↑(«expr ⊔ » s t) : set α) = s ∪ t :=
  rfl
#align coe_sup coe_sup
coe_mk:
@[simp]
theorem coe_mk (s : clopens α) (h) : (mk s h : set α) = s :=
  rfl
#align coe_mk coe_mk
coe_inf:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⊓ » -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_inf (s t : clopen_upper_set α) : (↑(«expr ⊓ » s t) : set α) = s ∩ t :=
  rfl
#align coe_inf coe_inf
coe_bot:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr⊥» -/
@[simp]
theorem coe_bot : (↑(«expr⊥» : clopen_upper_set α) : set α) = ∅ :=
  rfl
#align coe_bot coe_bot
clopen:
theorem clopen (s : clopen_upper_set α) : is_clopen (s : set α) :=
  s.clopen'
#align clopen clopen
